    <item>
      <title>由于销售增长放缓，全球基金出售联合利华印度股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/foreign-holding-in-hindustan-unilever-drops-to-four-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于印度斯坦联合利华有限公司 (Hindustan Unilever Ltd.) 面临消费者需求疲软和竞争加剧的局面，全球投资者已将其持股量降至四年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/foreign-holding-in-hindustan-unilever-drops-to-four-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券牛市推动中国信贷收益率跌至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-credit-yields-drop-to-record-lows-on-bond-bull-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者在流动性充沛的金融体系中大量购买公司债券以提高回报，中国的本地信贷收益率已降至有史以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-credit-yields-drop-to-record-lows-on-bond-bull-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库存数据和伊朗制裁成为焦点，油价保持上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于报告显示美国原油库存减少，且交易商追踪对伊朗实施新制裁的进展，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 23:27:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市上涨，澳元因 CPI 上涨而上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国科技股上涨和新的经济数据重新燃起人们对美国降息的希望之后，亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国石油买家将承受美国对伊朗更严厉的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-oil-buyers-set-to-weather-tighter-us-sanctions-on-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的私营炼油厂可能会寻求购买更多来源不明的货物，以准备应对美国对伊朗出口的新制裁，以确保原油继续流向世界最大进口国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-oil-buyers-set-to-weather-tighter-us-sanctions-on-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼卢比暴跌可能导致印尼在 2025 年之前无法降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/rupiah-slump-may-keep-bank-indonesia-rate-cuts-at-bay-until-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚央行可能会将货币宽松政策推迟到今年晚些时候，甚至是 2025 年初，因为它正在等待美联储利率路径的不确定性和中东持续的战斗结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/rupiah-slump-may-keep-bank-indonesia-rate-cuts-at-bay-until-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
